_:N733f8d58780c4c0b9de1bb8f8d4d8088 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Emma is an accomplished commercial leader who began her career at Nuclear Restoration Services (NRS) in the late 1990s.</p>\n\n<p>After working extensively across the NDA group and with government stakeholders, Emma rejoined NRS in 2019 to lead the Future Missions team.</p>\n\n<p>In 2023 Emma became the Commercial Director for NRS, joining the NRS Executive team. Emma champions diversity and inclusivity and serves as the Executive Sponsor for the NRS Women’s Network.</p>\n" .
